Description:
    Overloaded controler generator. Sets up controllers to use coteyr_pack
    and and builds some basic default views

Example:
    ./script/generate controller ExamplesControler
    ./script/generate controller examples_controller

    This will create:
        /app/controllers
        /app/helpers
        /app/helpers/examples_helper.rb
        /app/views
        /app/views/examples_controller
        /app/views/examples_controller/_example.html.erb
        /app/views/examples_controller/edit.html.erb
        /app/views/examples_controller/index.html.erb
        /app/views/examples_controller/new.html.erb
        /app/views/examples_controller/show.html.erb
        /test/functional
        /test/functional/examples_controller_test.rb

